# Supplier Module — FROZEN

**Frozen:** 2026-06-22 (develop branch, pre-production deploy)

The Supplier module is approved for freeze. Do not modify Supplier-related code without explicit user approval.

## Scope

- Supplier CRUD, status (active/inactive), soft delete, restore
- Supplier form UI layout (frozen)
- Profile photo, card front/back document uploads with storage cleanup
- Mobile number registry and supplier code sequencing
- Role-based permissions via `users.role` (`super_admin` | `staff`)

## Out of scope (deferred)

- Full Roles & Permissions module (placeholder page only)
- Customer module (blocked until Supplier deploy is complete)
- Ledger account auto-link on supplier create

## Operational query for future modules

```php
Supplier::operational()->orderBy('business_name')
```

Excludes inactive and soft-deleted suppliers from Purchase dropdowns.
